{
  "info": {
    "name": "RemoteOffice API (Updated)",
    "_postman_id": "d4a3b1f0-remoteoffice-collection",
    "description": "Postman collection for RemoteOffice backend with hierarchical role system and project management.\n\nRole Hierarchy:\n- Superadmin: Can create companies and assign company admins\n- Company Admin: Can add users (employees/members) to their specific company, create/manage projects and tasks\n- Employee/Member: Regular users within a company, can update assigned tasks\n\nAPI Structure (Updated):\n- Auth routes handle company/user creation and management\n- Company routes handle profile updates and media uploads\n- Tasks routes handle task management (CRUD, status updates, filtering)\n- Projects routes handle project management (CRUD, member management)\n- Dashboard routes handle analytics and statistics\n\nEnvironment Variables Required:\n- baseUrl: API base URL (e.g., http://localhost:5000)\n- token: JWT token for authentication\n- SUPERADMIN_SECRET: Secret code for superadmin registration\n- companyId: Company ID for company-specific operations\n- taskId: Task ID for task-specific operations\n- projectId: Project ID for project-specific operations\n- userId: User ID for user-specific operations",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
